description: Zalgoify the last message! Use like {{prefix}}zalgo *n*, where n is a integer from 1 to 10.
invalidNum: You specified an invalid number (or something that isn't a number) in your command {{prefix}}zalgo {{subcommand}}. **Pro tip**: when I say "an integer from 1 to 10", I mean *one of* 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, or 10.
